data.description: Check out this lovely two-story home located in Forest Heights.The beautiful curb appeal invites you into 2,740 sqft. With 4-5 bedrooms, 3 baths, high ceiling & open living area.The kitchen features maple cabinets, and granite counter tops. On the 1st floor you will find two secondary bedrooms, the primary bedroom; en-suite bath with walk in large closet. Double sinks, separate shower and great size soaker tub to take off the stress of the day! Upstairs you have the 3rd secondary bedroom plus the bonus living area which can be used as a game room, office or even a bedroom. This home has perfect amount of space for every member of your family! Let’s not forget the oversized backyard with no back neighbors. With the covered patio and pool this home is perfect for entertaining!
